<title>UK: BZW sets warrants on Alliance &amp; Leicester.</title>
<headline>BZW sets warrants on Alliance &amp; Leicester.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>BZW Warrants Ltd has issued 50 million American-style call warrants, on Alliance &amp; Leicester Building Society, lead manager BZW Securities said.</p>
<p>One warrant controls one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    5.57 GBP		  ISSUE PRICE  0.8275 GBP</p>
<p> MATURITY DATE   20.OCT.98		 PAYDATE	14.MAY.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   LUXEMBOURG		MIN EXER LOT 100</p>
<p>SPOT REFERENCE  5.57 GBP</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
</text>
